# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ COMPOSITION-CASE-STUDIES  (real-world examples of F1..F6 multiplicative-composition)

  § CASE-1 : KAN-driven spectral-BRDF gradient-step (F1 + F4 + F5)
    setup     : Stage-6 spectral-BRDF needs differentiating-w.r.t. KAN-weights
                for inverse-rendering optimization-loop
    F1        : Jet<f32,2> stores primal-radiance + 1st-deriv-weight
    F4        : KAN-weights pre-baked-at-comptime via bake_kan
                @staged spectral-BRDF specializes per-band-config
    F5        : KAN-weights @on-device-only ; gradient-step IFC-clean
                no Sensitive<gaze> leaks into KAN-update
    composition: orthogonal — F1 differentiates F4-baked F5-IFC-clean values

  § CASE-2 : Foveated-render with gaze-saccade prediction (F1 + F5 + F6)
    setup     : Stage-2 gaze-collapse predicts saccade-velocity to drive
                fovea-mask Σ-update on next-frame
    F1        : Jet<f32,2> on gaze-velocity-stream produces 1st-deriv prediction
    F5        : gaze-stream tagged Sensitive<gaze> ; on-device-only
                TelemetryEgress::for_domain(Gaze) refuses egress
    F6        : path-hash-only logging if gaze-stream is fs-backed mock
    composition: F1 derivative on F5-tagged stream ; F6 logging-discipline

  § CASE-3 : Wave-Unity Phase-2 with conservation + comptime-bake (F3 + F4)
    setup     : Stage-4 wave-solver advances ψ-field with strict-conservation
    F3        : Conservation<ψ-norm> + Conservation<energy> rows on tick-fn
                Travel + Crystallize forbidden in same composition
    F4        : MockStabilityKan stage-1 fallback ; trained-Kan baked-at-comptime
                via bake_kan when training-loop completes (S12+)
    composition: F3 enforces conservation-laws ; F4 bakes optimization-table

  § CASE-4 : Σ-mask cell-touch with real-crypto audit (F5 + F6)
    setup     : OmegaField::set_cell mutates a Σ-claimed cell
    F5        : EnforcesΣAtCellTouches MIR-pass already-passed @ compile
                Phase-5 AGENCY-VERIFY runtime double-check confirms
    F6        : audit-chain entry signed-with Ed25519 ; BLAKE3 over field-state
                path-hash for fs-backed image-snapshot side-channel
    composition: F5 structural-gate + F6 cryptographic-audit-trail

